# cmake

## 安装

```sh
CMAKE_VERSION=3.17.0-rc2
curl -LO 'https://github.com/Kitware/CMake/releases/download/v3.17.0-rc2/cmake-$CMAKE_VERSION-Linux-x86_64.sh'
chmod u+x cmake-$CMAKE_VERSION-Linux-x86_64.sh
sudo ./cmake-$CMAKE_VERSION-Linux-x86_64.sh --skip-license --prefix=/usr/local
```

